txt.en: Thurindol can be found in the keep at Bâr Húrin.\n\nYou should talk to Thurindol.
'You found some supplies. Excellent work! I shall commend you to Anborn myself.'
You didn't find a Ranger cache here

'Years ago we buried supply caches within the rubble of Bâr Húrin and many other ruined towns in Southern Ithilien. Hiding our provisions allows us to move through Ithilien unnoticed by the enemy. Will you assist us by searching through the rubble in Bâr Húrin for any supplies we may have missed since establishing camp here?'
Thurindol asks you to assist the Rangers by searching through rubble in Bâr Húrin for any buried supplies.
Bâr Húrin is located in Southern Ithilien.\n\nYou should search rubble piles in Bâr Húrin for buried Ranger supplies.
